# YAML Metadata in files

The tool can read YAML metadata from each content file (.html or .md) in the following format

---
title: ...
content: ...
---

The YAML metadata must be at the beginning of the file. It will not be displayed in the final output

The YAML Metadata for this file is:

**title**: {{ current_page.data.title }}
**content**: {{ current_page.data.content }}
**description**: {{ current_page.data.description }}